ENTRY       EC 2.4.2.35                 Enzyme
NAME        flavonol-3-O-glycoside xylosyltransferase;
            UDP-D-xylose:flavonol-3-O-glycoside 2''-O-beta-D-xylosyltransferase
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Pentosyltransferases
SYSNAME     UDP-alpha-D-xylose:flavonol-3-O-glycoside 2''-O-beta-D-xylosyltransferase
REACTION    UDP-alpha-D-xylose + a flavonol 3-O-glycoside = UDP + a flavonol 3-[beta-D-xylosyl-(1->2)-beta-D-glycoside] [RN:R03268]
ALL_REAC    R03268 > R06811 R06814
SUBSTRATE   UDP-alpha-D-xylose [CPD:C00190];
            flavonol 3-O-glycoside
PRODUCT     UDP [CPD:C00015];
            flavonol 3-[beta-D-xylosyl-(1->2)-beta-D-glycoside] [CPD:C04069]
COMMENT     Flavonol 3-O-glucoside, flavonol 3-O-galactoside and, more slowly, rutin, can act as acceptors.
HISTORY     EC 2.4.2.35 created 1986, modified 2014
